@node CH_0A
@title "Introduction"
0A. introduction
----------------
E Developer Professional is a texteditor with an environment where
you can run, debug, profile and compile your program direct from a menu
choice.

Other feature:
If you, like me, always have to fix the "layout" of the program after
coding a couple of hours, you know how boring it is to delete spaces
and tabs and insert new ones to make the code look good. Now the problem
is solved, just press the "indent all icon" and your program gets a good
layout.

There is also an intelligent Auto indent function. Just press Return
after each line and let EDevProf fix the rest.

If you want the editor can show the keywords, strings, etc in different
colours to make the code more easy to read. 

A listview with all the procedures in the program. You can jump to a 
procedure with just a mouseclick.

Friendly userinterface to all the compiler options.

Userinterface to add, del and show modules.

Undo function.

@endnode
